我们从波函数
\begin_inset Formula $\psi_{k}^{\left(+\right)}\left(\sbf{r}\right)$
\end_inset

开始：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\psi_{k}^{\left(+\right)}\left(\sbf{r}\right) & =\langle\sbf r|\sbf k\rangle+\int\dif\sbf r^{\prime}\bra{\sbf r}\left(E_{k}-\hat{H}_{0}+i\varepsilon\right)^{-1}\ket{\sbf r^{\prime}}V\left(\sbf r^{\prime}\right)\langle\sbf r^{\prime}|\psi^{\left(+\right)}\rangle\\
 & =\langle\sbf r|\sbf k\rangle-\int\dif\sbf r^{\prime}G_{0}^{\left(+\right)}\left(\sbf r,\sbf r^{\prime}\right)U\left(\sbf r^{\prime}\right)\langle\sbf r^{\prime}|\psi^{\left(+\right)}\rangle\\
 & =\frac{1}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3/2}}e^{ikz}-\int\dif\sbf r^{\prime}\frac{e^{ik\abs*{\sbf r-\sbf r^{\prime}}}}{4\pi\abs*{\sbf r-\sbf r^{\prime}}}U\left(\sbf r^{\prime}\right)\psi_{\sbf k}^{\left(+\right)}\left(\sbf r\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

这里的约定是
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\langle\sbf r|\sbf k\rangle=\frac{1}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3/2}}e^{ikz}
\]

\end_inset

格林函数定义为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
G_{0}^{\left(+\right)}\left(\sbf r,\sbf r^{\prime}\right) & =\frac{-\hbar^{2}}{2\mu}\bra{\sbf r}\left(E_{k}-\hat{H}_{0}+i\varepsilon\right)^{-1}\ket{\sbf r^{\prime}}\\
 & =\frac{-\hbar^{2}}{2\mu}\int\frac{\dif\sbf k^{\prime}}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3}}\frac{e^{i\sbf k^{\prime}\cdot\left(\sbf r-\sbf r^{\prime}\right)}}{E_{k}-\frac{\hbar^{2}}{2\mu}\sbf k^{2}+i\varepsilon}\\
 & =-\int\frac{\dif\sbf k^{\prime}}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3}}\frac{e^{i\sbf k^{\prime}\cdot\left(\sbf r-\sbf r^{\prime}\right)}}{\sbf k^{2}-\sbf k^{\prime2}+i\varepsilon}\\
 & =\frac{1}{4\pi\abs*{\sbf r-\sbf r^{\prime}}}e^{ik\abs*{\sbf r-\sbf r^{\prime}}}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

当事件粒子进入势能的有效作用范围，波函数的形式应该是
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\psi_{\sbf k}^{\left(+\right)}\left(\sbf r\right)=\frac{1}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3/2}}\varphi\left(\sbf r\right)e^{ikz}
\]

\end_inset

把
\begin_inset Formula $\psi_{\sbf k}^{\left(+\right)}\left(\sbf r\right)$
\end_inset

代入方程：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\psi_{\sbf k}^{\left(+\right)}\left(\sbf r\right)=\frac{1}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3/2}}e^{ikz}-\int\dif\sbf r^{\prime}G_{0}^{\left(+\right)}\left(\sbf r,\sbf r^{\prime}\right)U\left(\sbf r^{\prime}\right)\psi_{\sbf k}^{\left(+\right)}\left(\sbf r^{\prime}\right)
\]

\end_inset

得到对
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi\left(\sbf r\right)$
\end_inset

的方程：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\varphi\left(\sbf r\right) & =1+\frac{1}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3}}\int\dif\sbf r^{\prime}\int\dif\sbf k^{\prime}\frac{e^{i\sbf k^{\prime}\cdot\left(\sbf r-\sbf r^{\prime}\right)}}{\sbf k^{2}-\sbf k^{\prime2}+i\varepsilon}U\left(\sbf r^{\prime}\right)\varphi\left(\sbf r^{\prime}\right)e^{i\sbf k\cdot\left(\sbf r^{\prime}-\sbf r\right)}\\
 & =1+\frac{1}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3}}\int\dif\sbf r^{\prime\prime}\int\dif\sbf k^{\prime}\frac{e^{i\left(\sbf k^{\prime}-\sbf k\right)\cdot\sbf r^{\prime\prime}}}{\sbf k^{2}-\sbf k^{\prime2}+i\varepsilon}U\left(\sbf r-\sbf r^{\prime\prime}\right)\varphi\left(\sbf r-\sbf r^{\prime\prime}\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\sbf r^{\prime}-\sbf r=\sbf r^{\prime\prime}$
\end_inset

。
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
G_{0}^{\left(+\right)}\left(\sbf r,\sbf r^{\prime}\right)=-\int\frac{\dif\sbf k^{\prime}}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3}}\frac{e^{i\sbf k^{\prime}\cdot\left(\sbf r-\sbf r^{\prime}\right)}}{\sbf k^{2}-\sbf k^{\prime2}+i\varepsilon}
\]

\end_inset

我们引入
\begin_inset Formula $\sbf\kappa=\sbf k^{\prime}-\sbf k$
\end_inset

，即散射矢量，
\begin_inset Formula $\sbf k^{\prime}=\sbf k+\sbf\kappa$
\end_inset

。然后我们得到：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & k^{\prime2}=\kappa^{2}+k^{2}+2\sbf k\cdot\sbf\kappa\approx k^{2}+2\sbf k\cdot\sbf\kappa\\
 & k^{\prime2}-k^{2}=-2\sbf k\cdot\sbf\kappa\\
 & \varphi\left(\sbf r\right)=1+\frac{1}{\left(2\pi\right)^{3}}\int\dif\sbf r^{\prime\prime}\int\dif\sbf\kappa\frac{e^{i\sbf\kappa\cdot\sbf r^{\prime\prime}}}{-2\sbf k\cdot\sbf\kappa+i\varepsilon}U\left(\sbf r-\sbf r^{\prime\prime}\right)\varphi\left(\sbf r-\sbf r^{\prime\prime}\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

我们注意到
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\int\dif\sbf\kappa\frac{e^{i\sbf\kappa\cdot\sbf r^{\prime\prime}}}{-2\sbf k\cdot\sbf\kappa+i\varepsilon} & =\int\dif\kappa_{x}e^{i\kappa_{x}x^{\prime\prime}}\int\dif\kappa_{y}e^{i\kappa_{y}x^{\prime\prime}}\int\dif\kappa_{z}e^{i\kappa_{z}x^{\prime\prime}}\frac{e^{i\kappa_{z}z^{\prime\prime}}}{-2k\,\kappa_{z}+i\varepsilon}\\
 & =\frac{-i}{2k}\left(2\pi\right)^{3}\delta\left(x^{\prime\prime}\right)\delta\left(y^{\prime\prime}\right)\Theta\left(z^{\prime\prime}\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

